# NAME: Spotify
# AUTHOR: steak
# TYPE: Quantumult X Filter
# DESCRIPTION: 音乐 / 播客 / CDN 分流规则
# SOURCE: Split from GlobalServices.list
# UPDATED: 2026-05-11
#
# ================================
# 使用说明
# ================================
# 1. 文件名：Spotify.list
# 2. 适用于：Quantumult X [filter_remote]
# 3. 策略组名称：Spotify
# 4. 本文件由原 GlobalServices.list 拆分，便于后续单独维护
# 5. IP-CIDR / IP6-CIDR 已追加 no-resolve
#
# QX 远程订阅示例：
# https://raw.githubusercontent.com/reverie1988/QX/refs/heads/main/Rules/Spotify.list, tag=Spotify, force-policy=Spotify, update-interval=172800, opt-parser=false, enabled=true
#
# ================================
# 规则统计
# ================================
# HOST: 6
# HOST-SUFFIX: 20
# HOST-KEYWORD: 1
# USER-AGENT: 1
# IP-CIDR: 2
# IP6-CIDR: 0
# IP-ASN: 0
# TOTAL: 30
#
# ================================
# 规则内容
# ================================
# Spotify
# ================================
